\keywords{Finsler metrics, sprays, linear connections, family of affine connections, second variation of energy functional}


\begin{abstract}
We propose a unified approach to the theory of connections in the geometry of sprays and Finsler metrics which, in particular,
gives a simple explanation of the well-known fact that all the classical Finslerian connections provide exactly the same formulas appearing in
the calculus of variations.
\end{abstract}

